梅尔·吉布森（Mel Gibson）感谢小罗伯特·唐尼（Robert Downey Jr.）在反犹太主义丑闻之后的支持https://www.nme.com/news/film/mel-gibson-thanks-robert-downey-jr-for-support-following-anti-semitism-scandal-3615414?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=mel-gibson-谢谢 - 罗伯特 -  downey-jr-for-for-for-spport-follow-tollow-anti-semitism-ScandalElizabeth Aubrey Tue, 09 Apr 2024 13:49:17 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3615414 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="罗伯特·唐尼（Robert Downey Jr）和梅尔·吉布森（Mel Gibson）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “他站起来为我说话。这是一个大胆而慷慨和善良的姿态”</p><p>梅尔·吉布森（Mel Gibson）的后，感谢小罗伯特·唐尼（Robert Downey Jr.）在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/mel-gibson-thanks-robert-downey-jr-for-support-following-anti-semitism-scandal-3615414">反犹太主义丑闻后的支持</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="罗伯特·唐尼（Robert Downey Jr）和梅尔·吉布森（Mel Gibson）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mel-gibson">梅尔·吉布森（Mel Gibson）</a>感谢<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rober-downey-jr">小罗伯特·唐尼（Robert Downey Jr.）</a>在过去的丑闻之后的支持，因为他因反犹太主义而被捕。</p><p>在<a href="https://www.esquire.com/entertainment/a60314472/robert-downey-jr-interview-2024/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>《时尚》</i></a>中出现的唐尼（Downey Jr.）的一个新封面故事中，吉布森（Gibson）将唐尼（Downey）称为“大胆，慷慨和善良”，敦促好莱坞遵循他在2006年的反犹太评论，以宽恕他。</p><p>吉布森告诉<em>《时尚》</em> ：“有一次，我遇到了一个棘手的情况，这已经结束了我的职业生涯。” “我在警车后座喝醉了，说了一些蠢话，然后突然间：被列入黑名单。我是被取消的海报男孩。</p><p> “ [罗伯特]几年来邀请我获得他获得的某种奖项 - 我们总是拥有这种望远镜的东西，如果他在货车上，我就掉下来了，如果我在旅​​行车上，他跌倒了。”</p><p>他继续说：“所以当时我在好莱坞几乎不存在，他站起来为我说话。这是一个大胆、慷慨和善意的举动。我因此而爱他。” </p><figure id="attachment_3615418" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3615418" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3615418" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-Photo-by-Eric-Charbonneau_WireImage.jpg" alt="罗伯特·唐尼（Robert Downey Jr）和梅尔·吉布森（Mel Gibson）" width="2000" height="1269" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-Photo-by-Eric-Charbonneau_WireImage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-Photo-by-Eric-Charbonneau_WireImage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-Photo-by-Eric-Charbonneau_WireImage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-Photo-by-Eric-Charbonneau_WireImage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-Photo-by-Eric-Charbonneau_WireImage-1392x883.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Robert-Downey-Jr-and-Mel-Gibson-Photo-by-Eric-Charbonneau_WireImage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3615418" class="wp-caption-text"> Robert Downey Jr和Mel Gibson  - 信用：Eric Charbonneau/WireImage/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>吉布森（Gibson）参考了2011年美国电影院颁奖典礼，小唐尼（Downey Jr.</p><p>他要求好莱坞加入他“宽恕我的朋友他的侵入，给予[吉布森]，就像你给我一样干净的板岩，并允许他继续对我们的集体艺术的伟大和持续的贡献，而没有羞耻”，指的是他的法律麻烦。在90年代，导致他入狱。</p><p>在其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/robert-downey-jr-would-happily-play-iron-man-again-3614939">小唐尼（Downey Jr.）最近透露，如果机会出现，他将返回漫威电影宇宙</a>。</p><p>他因在10部电影中担任《钢铁侠》（Iron Man）的主演，与<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/avengers-endgame"><em>《复仇者联盟：2019年的最后游戏》（Avengers）</em></a>一起获得了全球认可。</p><p>早在三月份，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/oscars-2024-winners-full-list-3599250">小唐尼就凭借</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/christopher-nolan">克里斯托弗·诺兰</a>广受好评的传记片《<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/oppenheimer-review-christopher-nolan-3470392"><em>奥本海默</em></a>》中扮演刘易斯·施特劳斯一角，赢得了他的第一个奥斯卡最佳男配角奖。</p><p>梅尔·吉布森（Mel Gibson）的后，感谢小罗伯特·唐尼（Robert Downey Jr.）在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/mel-gibson-thanks-robert-downey-jr-for-support-following-anti-semitism-scandal-3615414">反犹太主义丑闻后的支持</a>。</p> ;
